description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Basildon &amp; Brentwood CCG Continuing Healthcare Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complex Case manager Band 7 x 0.6 wte (22.5 hrs per week)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Basildon and Brentwood CCG is responsible for commissioning healthcare for the population of Basildon, Billericay, Brentwood and Wickford, which has a total population of 280,000. As a CCG we work in six neighbourhoods, with 35 member practices and work collaboratively with Essex County Council.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our main providers are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basildon and Thurrock Hospital (BTUH) – for whom we are the lead commissioner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Barking Havering and Redbridge Hospitals (BHRT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;North East London Foundation Trust (NELFT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Essex Partnership Trust Community and Mental Health services (EPUT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;East of England Ambulance Service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The post holder is required to be a Registered Nurse or Allied Health Professional.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work within the Continuing Healthcare Team to implement the National Framework for NHS Continuing Healthcare, Funded Nursing Care and Personal Health Budgets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key qualities required for the post are excellent communication and educational skills at all levels in a multidisciplinary forum and with service users and carers. Ability to negotiate in complex situations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The CCG is committed to evolve to provide a 7-day a week access to services and applicants should be prepared to work flexibly. Applicants should also be able to travel between patients, a car driver is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like more information; please contact &lt;strong&gt;Stephanie Williams, Clinical Team Leader on 01268 594635 or &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;s.williams10@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date is: &lt;strong&gt;27/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews are on: &lt;strong&gt;TBC&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
